{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_01","textHome":"プロミストブラッドの一員、鈴鹿さくやだよ\n。神浜の学校には最近転校してきたんだ。\nあー、転校の理由は言えないんだけど、や\nましいことはないよ！…君、神浜の魔法少\n女、だよね？穏便に済ませたいって思って\nるなら、私に深く関わらない方がいいかも\nよ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_17","textHome":"アオはただのゲーマーじゃないよ。ゲームだ\nけじゃなく、リアルでも頭が切れてて必ず\n勝てる作戦を考えてくれるし、すごく頼り\nになるんだ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_18","textHome":"結菜…前は、怒りで我を忘れるような子じゃ\nなかったのに…。でも、優しいところは変\nわってない。いつか、元の結菜に戻るよね\n…？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_19","textHome":"おっ!?今、わかっちゃったかも！あれだ、\nゾーンに入るってやつだ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_20","textHome":"うー…んっ、気持ちいーい！体に力がみなぎ\nってきたよ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_21","textHome":"魔女もグリーフシードもなかった頃の二木に\n比べれば、今はずっとマシだよ。三姉妹に\nついていけば必ず救われるって、希望を持\nてるからね！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_22","textHome":"チームの今後のことは、結菜たち三姉妹が決\nめることだから、私は私にできることをす\nるよ。…まぁ、結菜をサポートするぐらい\nしかできないけど、必要としてくれる限り\n、私は結菜と共に居続けるよ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_23","textHome":"魔法少女同士で争うなんて、できるならした\nくないよ。だけど、結菜やひかるや…仲間\nたちを傷つけるヤツが居る限り、私は戦う\nしかないんだ。たとえ私が敵う相手じゃな\nくても…完全燃焼するまで止まらない…！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_24","textHome":"おーっす！今日はどの部位を鍛える？OK、\nハムストリングね！筋トレは精神力も鍛え\nてくれるからね、魔法少女にも効果あるか\nもしれないよ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_25","textHome":"おはよー！私はジョギングに行くとこだけど\n、もちろん一緒に来るよね!?運動してか\nら食べる朝ご飯って、最っ高だもんね！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_26","textHome":"くぅぅ…お腹空いたぁ～。…よしっ、早弁し\nちゃおっとー。…えっ、フツーするよね？\n育ち盛りの女子なら、みんなやってるよね\n!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_02","textHome":"初めまして！私、鈴鹿さくや！さくやって呼\nんでよ。…あーゴメン、馴れ馴れしかった\nかな？迷惑かけないようにするから、とに\nかくよろしくね！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_27","textHome":"あ、部活の時間だ！よーし、今日も気合入れ\nて、いっちょ激走しちゃいますかー！…っ\nてダメダメ！目立たないようにしないと…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_28","textHome":"さて、寝よーう！強くなるためには、睡眠も\n重要な要素だからね。あっ!?宿題…やっ\nてない…けど！明日の私が頑張るはず！よ\nし、寝よーう！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_29","textHome":"最近は体を鍛える女子が増えてるらしいよ！\nようやく時代が私に追いついて…ハッ！追\nいつかれたらダメだよね！ぶっちぎりで突\nき放さなきゃ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_30","textHome":"さーて、活動、活動…。あ、もちろん、魔女\n退治のことだよ！それ以外の意味なんてあ\nるわけないし！んじゃ、パトロールにしゅ\nっぱーつ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_31","textHome":"「果てなしのミラーズ」で私のコピーに会っ\nたら、一度はスピード勝負してみたいな。\n「最大の敵は自分」って言うしね！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_32","textHome":"何度やっても、チーム戦は緊張するね。私の\nヘマでみんなをピンチに巻き込むわけには\nいかないし。…ふぅ、気を引き締めていこ\nう！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_33","textHome":"大丈夫、やればできる！今は不安でも、自信\nなんてあとからついてくる！いけるいける\n！頑張れ頑張れ！ゴールはもうすぐそこだ\nー！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_34","textHome":"そろそろ引っ越しバイトに応募しようと思っ\nてるんだよね！家族には転校したいってワ\nガママ聞いてもらったし、少しでも恩を返\nさなきゃ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_35","textHome":"はぁ…大丈夫かなぁ…実家のスニーカーコレ\nクション。いや、そりゃあ心配だよ！私が\n目を離すと、お母さんが勝手に履こうとす\nるしさ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_36","textHome":"ぬ、ぐぅぅ…食べたいぃっ…イヤ！我慢我慢\n…！ラーメンは太る…ラーメンは筋肉にな\nらない…けどラーメンはウマい…あぁ！食\nべたいッ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_03","textHome":"う～ん…困ったなぁ…これからどうしよう？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_37","textHome":"ああ、もう！なんでこうも、「臨機応変」と\nか「柔軟」って言葉が似合わないかなー！\nらんかみたいにうまくやりたいのに…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":300}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_38","textHome":"あー…やれやれ…。次女は人使いが荒いなー\n。まぁ、頼まれ事の難易度が高いほど、私\nも燃えてくるんだけどさ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_39","textHome":"たまに…怖い夢を見るんだ。昔の友だちが、\n追いかけて来る夢…。私が…、…いや、何\nでもないよ…何でもない…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_40","textHome":"れ、恋愛なんて私全然わからないよ！昔好き\nな人は居たけど「好き！」って告白したら\n速攻断られて玉砕したっていうかああもう\n何言ってんの私!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_41","textHome":"…998、999、1000！はぁぁ、終わ\nったー…！筋トレのこの達成感が好きなん\nだよね～！さーて、腹筋さんは～…うん、\n見事な仕上がりだよ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_42","textHome":"最初から飛ばしてくよ！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_43","textHome":"うん、良い風吹いてたね！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_44","textHome":"おっ？大会記録更新っ！"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_45","textHome":"10秒台も夢じゃない！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_46","textHome":"次は世界記録目指してこー！"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_04","textHome":"うーんと、今日の報告事項は…特になし！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_05","textHome":"くーっ！１日の締めのラーメン、しみるな～"}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_13","textHome":"ふぅ、やっとウォーミングアップ完了ってト\nコかな。まだまだ鍛えるよ！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_14","textHome":"おっし！今日の練習メニュー完了！あとは追\n加で何をやろっかな～！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":1}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_15","textHome":"陸上の思い出は色々あるけど、あの大会のこ\nとは忘れられないな…。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":302100}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3021_00_16","textHome":"樹里やらんかとは、同じチームになってから\n少し気まずい時もあったけど、今は同じ目\n的のためにうまく連携して動けてるよ"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302100,"motion":200}]}]},"version":3}